My music project, Resident Entity is almost finished. 
It surprises me more everyday as  the songs start taking shape and hearing the genre that they slowly and organically morph into. 
This is fun for me because I never thought I‚Äôd really be making my own music. I‚Äôve never taken a class, grew up playing instruments, and I barely know the chord names. I kinda just feel it out and see where it goes and that‚Äôs also been super exciting for me.
To take something that‚Äôs essentially nothing, just floating around inside my mind, and paint that out into something. 
Life is super neat like that. It just exists here and there. Inside and outside our minds. Within the context of our experiences, emotions, thoughts, and existence. Just waiting there for us. 
More about the actual project sooner than later like genres blended, album name, etc. 
Next up for me, finish the last little nuances and other details.
